{"tid":2422821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中槍「熊仔餅」腸黏連再入院","createTime":"2021-02-25T13:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T13:10:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48bcc5cc76b2a324adad84e8152ec9893366c545","tid":2422821,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/H4HQRLHGQRGW3HQX7JKOBBHGTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FH4HQRLHGQRGW3HQX7JKOBBHGTM%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=053478c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FH4HQRLHGQRGW3HQX7JKOBBHGTM%2F&h=0ef1f53d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/H4HQRLHGQRGW3HQX7JKOBBHGTM/</a><br />\n<br />\n中槍「熊仔餅」腸黏連再入院<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CfnEkTa9H_eB9mPNXSIUMWda8GM=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4DT5WCHYC5A6NII6UOPZ74K34E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCfnEkTa9H_eB9mPNXSIUMWda8GM%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4DT5WCHYC5A6NII6UOPZ74K34E.jpg&h=c48cdd82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前年11月「熊仔餅」在西灣河遭警員近距離槍擊，至今仍受後遺症困擾。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前年11月西灣河中槍21歲青年「熊仔餅」周柏均，近日病情反復，藝人阮民安昨晚引述熊仔餅友人的消息發帖文，指熊仔餅因為腸黏連問題，要再度入院，可能今日早上需要接受手術。<br />\n<br />\n熊仔餅昨深夜接受本報訪問時語氣虛弱，不願就病情談及太多，但承認入院是與中槍後腸黏連的後遺症有關，着記者今日再聯絡他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n精神差兼不時疼痛<br />\n<br />\n根據熊仔餅Instagram限時動態，可見他昨日身處病榻，他向記者表示身在私家醫院，但留醫期間仍透過IG與支持者互動。<br />\n<br />\n熊仔餅在IG提到自己近日倉卒入院，沒有帶齊東西解悶；又說自己精神較差，並不時疼痛，醫院要求他禁食，已有超過40小時沒有進食。另外他又指病房嘈吵，難以入睡，希望能盡快出院「燒嘢食」。<br />\n<br />\n前年11月11日全港三罷，有抗爭者同時發動「黎明行動」，當日熊仔餅在西灣河遭警員連開三槍近距離擊中。熊仔餅中槍之後病情一直反復，據他上月facebook帖文，指槍傷後至今逾年仍受後遺症困擾，包括嚴重痛症，痛至「食不到止痛藥」兼嘔吐不斷，骨折亦未康復，近數周更經常夢到當天中槍情景。"},{"pid":"de3e435c5281e601449e5d0a728f3aad32591035","tid":2422821,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678064eb48c0353e41a24ae0bb134517c711fd33","tid":2422821,"uid":53364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"撐住啊"},{"pid":"52ebe4c5c96d496e2ac3482bdf4c12723989d315","tid":2422821,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">關</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a528c91d6b9abfd47aa15fb376aa465d1528786","tid":2422821,"uid":392566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂住"},{"pid":"f109e7daba2695c849e21f5f34a47c614b3b24f4","tid":2422821,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"「熊仔餅」中槍夢魘 骨折、劇痛難久站  3.23上庭 盼手足聲援<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2382267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2382267</a>"},{"pid":"16e4abb36c8d67a100502886675151d4e60e3799","tid":2422821,"uid":202754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"11b6ca99f01d568500e126677a266197262a260e","tid":2422821,"uid":189046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撐住,祝早日康復"}]}